{
  "stem": "6159.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he obtained a letter from them that we are responsible for employment for, for the husband, and that's how we could get out of there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were there not longer than two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went to, to see this friend, and we were staying with them until we get into the-- a boarding house where we rented a room.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we started to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the luck wasn't with us because my son has had a rheumatic fever when he was already-- we were here for a couple of years-- no, first year.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No, the first person who got sick-- I was a sick with thyroid problem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My eyes was bulging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My heart was beating 120 at a minute, and my neck was swollen, and I still had to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went to a factory which is called Harrison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My husband was working there also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was doing the tools on the machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was packing the tools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had a key money flat in [INAUDIBLE] got this opposite the park.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a bachelor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it was one bedroom, and so-called lunchroom together divided with the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The kitchen was just a strip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was working in different factor-- factories until he reached-- went to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he did night shift as well as day shift many a times, so we hardly met because I was working in a dress factory, finishing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "After-- I never had a needle in my hand, but after two or three jobs, they throw me out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They finally I find-- [LAUGHS] I learned how to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened is, one day that he was going with six other fellows in a truck-- motor truck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a closed-- a station wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
